## Environment Variable Reference

### Core

| Variable | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| `{{ project_slug | upper }}_ENVIRONMENT` | `str` | `local` | Deployment environment (`local`, `dev`, `test`, `staging`, `prod`) |
| `{{ project_slug | upper }}_DEBUG` | `bool` | `false` | Enable debug mode |
| `{{ project_slug | upper }}_LOG_LEVEL` | `str` | `INFO` | Logging level (`DEBUG`, `INFO`, `WARNING`, `ERROR`) |
| `{{ project_slug | upper }}_ALLOWED_ORIGINS` | `list[str]` | `["http://localhost:5173"]` | CORS allowed origins (JSON array) |
| `{{ project_slug | upper }}_SECRET_KEY` | `str` | *(required)* | Application secret key |
